Package: lesiontools
Type: Package
Title: Statistical and Computational Tools for Brain Lesion Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Jordan D.", family = "Dworkin",  
  email = "jdwor@mail.med.upenn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Jordan D. Dworkin <jdwor@mail.med.upenn.edu>
Description: Functions for the analysis of brain images, specifically in the presence of white-matter lesions. The package includes tools for obtaining image gradients and hessian matrices, finding veins in the brain, counting distinct lesions, and detecting central vein sign.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/jdwor/lesiontools
